        <h1>Welcome to the AWS Feature Roll (Features)</h1>
        <p>There are lot of services and features being released every week on the AWS platform. Keeping track about what's happening
	  can be challenging sometimes. Querying all feature announcements or creating a ready-to-go slide deck is now as simple as</p>
	<p>
	  <code>$ wget &ldquo;awsfeatureroll.elasticbeanstalk.com/api/feature?cat=compute&startdate=2015-01-01&enddate=2015-05-15&rdquo; &gt; releases.json </code>
	</p>
	<p>
	  <code>$ wget &ldquo;awsfeatureroll.elasticbeanstalk.com/api/slides?startdate=2015-06-01&enddate=2015-07-01</code>
	</p>
      </div>
